<p>4.<a class="anchor_link" href="#our-legal-basis">OUR LEGAL BASIS FOR PROCESSING DATA</a></p>

<p>5.<a class="anchor_link" href="#what-we-communicate">WHAT WE COMMUNICATE WITH YOU ABOUT</a></p>

<p>6.<a class="anchor_link" href="#marketing-preferences">MARKETING PREFERENCES</a></p>

<p>7.<a class="anchor_link" href="#who-we-share-your-data-with">WHO WE SHARE YOUR DATA WITH</a></p>

<p>8.<a class="anchor_link" href="#how-we-keep-your-data-safe">HOW WE KEEP YOUR DATA SAFE</a></p>

