<p>10.<a class="anchor_link" href="#how-long-we-keep-your-data-for">HOW LONG WE KEEP YOUR DATA FOR</a></p>

<p>11.<a class="anchor_link" href="#how-to-find-out-what-information">HOW TO FIND OUT WHAT INFORMATION WE HAVE ABOUT YOU</a></p>

<p>12.<a class="anchor_link" href="#how-to-change-the-way-we-contact-you">HOW TO CHANGE THE WAY WE CONTACT YOU</a></p>

<p>13.<a class="anchor_link" href="#what-to-do"> WHAT TO DO IF YOU DON’T WANT US TO PROCESS INFORMATION ABOUT YOU</a></p>

<p>14.<a class="anchor_link" href="#your-rights">YOUR RIGHTS</a></p>

<p>15.<a class="anchor_link" href="#changes-to-this-policy">CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</a></p>

